* 2010 : Disney animated project ''Princess Academy''.<ref>(21 August 2012) [http://disneyandmore.blogspot.com/2012/08/princess-academy-great-animated-short.html « Disney Animated Princess Academy"]. ''Disney and more''. Retrieved 21 August 2012.</ref><ref>(14 May 2013) [https://www.buzzfeed.com/briangalindo/disneys-princess-academy-an-amazing-animated-short-that-neve#.gcaG4BpXr « Olivier Ciappa's feature Princess Academy"]. ''Buzz Feed''. Retrieved 14 May 2013.</ref>
Music composed by 8 times Academy Award winner Alan Menken. The movie project was transformed into the global Disney phenomenon TV show "Princess Sofia"

=== Stage Director ===
* 2006 : ''Revolution’’. Musical.
* 2007 : ''Le Cabaret des Hommes Perdus’’. Musical. Winner of best musical and best author at the Molières Awards

